      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement, addressing a critical platform weak point, while the suspension utilizes Bilstein dampers for optimized lateral grip. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the internal components are within tight tolerances. Expect a visceral driving experience with linear power delivery and precise turn-in; a well-maintained driver\u2019s car with minor cosmetic patina that doesn't detract from its performance capabilities.",
